3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a strategy to constrain the load to some maximum value, which is a control problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with data offloading, which is a common problem in multimedia applications. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses load coupling and optimization, which are common topics in distributed and parallel computing.
